Frost! Frost!

279
00:22:14,471 --> 00:22:15,931
Aah!

280
00:22:15,973 --> 00:22:18,100
Wierzbowski!

281
00:22:18,142 --> 00:22:19,351
Wierzbowski!

282
00:22:19,393 --> 00:22:20,936
Aah!

283
00:22:20,978 --> 00:22:22,938
Let's rock!

284
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:24,606
