297
00:22:53,010 --> 00:22:54,887
All after "incinerator."

298
00:22:54,928 --> 00:22:58,974
Lay down a suppressing fire
with the incinerators...

299
00:22:59,016 --> 00:23:00,350
and fall back...

300
00:23:04,271 --> 00:23:06,148
Aah!

301
00:23:06,190 --> 00:23:07,316
Sarge!

302
00:23:07,357 --> 00:23:10,611
Apone, talk to me.

303
00:23:10,652 --> 00:23:12,279
Apone? Talk to me!

304
00:23:12,321 --> 00:23:13,489
He's gone!

305
00:23:15,157 --> 00:23:17,618
Get them out of there!

306
00:23:17,659 --> 00:23:19,411
Shut up!

307
00:23:19,453 --> 00:23:21,205
Hicks, whoever's left,
get the hell-

308
00:23:21,246 --> 00:23:22,623
-Shut up!
-God damn it!

309
00:23:24,374 --> 00:23:26,001
Where's Apone?!

310
00:23:26,043 --> 00:23:27,169
Where's Apone?!

311
00:23:27,211 --> 00:23:30,631
The Sarge is gone!
Let's get the fuck out of here!

312
00:23:30,672 --> 00:23:32,299
Let's go, Marines!

